# REALISTIC LOAN APPROVAL INSIGHT 
## Project Overview
This project analyzes loan application data to uncover key factors influencing loan approval and rejection decisions. Using data visualization techniques, the dashboard provides actionable insights into applicant behavior, financial profiles, and approval trends to support better decision-making.
The project was built as part of my data analysis learning journey and demonstrates my ability to transform raw data into meaningful business insights.
### Objectives
Analyze approved vs rejected loan applications
Identify factors influencing loan approval (Income, Credit Score, Loan Amount, Employment)
Visualize trends using interactive dashboards
Support realistic loan approval decision-making
 ## Dataset Description
The dataset contains anonymized loan application records with the following key fields:
Applicant ID
Loan Status (Approved / Rejected)
Annual Income
Credit Score
Loan Amount
Employment Length
Year
## Tools & Technologies Used
Microsoft Power BI ‚Äì Data modeling & interactive dashboards
