## Key Visualizations
Approved vs Rejected Loans (Bar Chart)
Loan Approval Trend by Year
Income vs Loan Status
Credit Score Impact on Loan Approval
KPI Cards:
Total Applications
Total Approved Loans
Total Loan Amount
Average Annual Income
## Key Insights
Applicants with higher credit scores and stable income had higher approval rates
Large loan amounts showed a higher rejection tendency
Employment length positively influenced loan approval
Approval rates varied significantly across years
## Dashboard Features
Interactive slicers (Year, Loan Status)
Dynamic KPIs
Clean and professional layout
Business-focused storytelling
## Project Outcome
This project strengthened my skills in:
Data cleaning & transformation
Pivot table analysis
Power BI visualization & storytelling
Business insight communication
